uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.charts.strategy

Class HashMapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.charts.strategy.HashMapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of object being mapped
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Labelled, LabelledSetRangeMapper<T>, PlotStrategy, RangeMapper<T>, SetRangeMapper<T>

    public class HashMapper<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements LabelledSetRangeMapper<T>
    HashMapper base class for LabeledTransform Mappers that builds the label vector and the mappings as data is seen. Sets are ordered according to the order the first data from that set was seen. The Rangemapper interface is provided by composition
